text: Carolyn Lawrence (born February 13, 1967) is an American television and voice actress mostly known for her voice role as Sandy Cheeks in Spongebob Squarepants, and Cindy Vortex in The Adventures of Jimmy Neutron: Boy Genius. Lawrence was born in Baltimore, Maryland on February 13, 1967. ==Other websites== * * Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:American voice actors Category:American television actors Category:Actors from Baltimore
